BTCworkers is a freelancing board that deals with payments through bitcoins only. BTCworkers first launched its public beta on November 3rd, 2012. 

Employers can post project listings, and freelancers can bid on them. Once an employer has selected a bid, they can then use escrow to fund the project. Some features include full site SSL and payment escrow. 

